Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:55.81,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}The kindness that he once saw is now gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:06.94,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)}He steps forward alone, looking only at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:22.29,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)\3c&HCB6D14&\bord2\blur2}He always listened to the song that disappeared by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:37.35,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(0,500)}He chased forever those footprints we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, perhaps, by my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko pikopikopiko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That imprint might remain for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise, Kunisaki-san, Kamio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened when Kano was still small.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first summer after our mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, balloons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.97,Note,,0,0,0,,[Store sign: Balloons]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, if I buy that, will I able to fly in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If a person could float upward with just one balloon, that yatai would be flying in the sky by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means that I can fly in the sky if I have lots of balloons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, you might be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can only afford one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's one balloon, we'll just have to blow it up really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, it'll be able to pick up much heavier things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to buy anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, thank you, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano wanted to fly in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because she believed that she could see her mother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her that her mother was in the sky and that she was watching over her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Father and I couldn't tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...that her mother was no longer anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's playing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We returned the feather to where we found it and went home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't go to where Mummy is anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano began to act strangely from the next day on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She started to fear bright lights, to unconsciously wander around outside, and to mumble meaningless words to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One night, Kano was gone before I realised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After I quickly looked for her, I found her in this examination room, pressing a scalpel against her own wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We treated it quickly, so it didn't become critical,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but at that time, I thought it wasn't Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that someone else was pretending to be Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a case of multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a mysterious bandanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep wearing it until you're an adult, you'll be able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no matter what happens, never take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were the one who gave Kano the bandanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My childish heart thought that if she ever tried to unconsciously cut her wrist, she'd see the bandanna and come to her senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano doesn't remember it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There was never such a thing as magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to follow in my father's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that I'd be able to cure Kano's disease someday if I became a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the feather that Kano touched?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apparently something in the shrine passed down from long ago; even the caretaker doesn't know the specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's the curse of that feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As a doctor, I can't accept that as the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a chance that the feather was the psychological trigger that caused the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, Kano bore a heavy burden in her heart after losing her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was probably the root cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to Kirishima-san's place today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I have my part-time job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll visit her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad that you made a new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I saw another dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream of flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that dream, I was travelling further and further back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was grieving far above the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Grieving?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, my body was soaring in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I, enclosed by the beautiful, comforting wind, feel so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aren't smiling, I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito Kunisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing that to collect garbage or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Collecting things in places like this is my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most pathetic hobby ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to hang around every day. You're in a really enviable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty much like that yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, I'm going to my part-time job to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that by any chance, Tohno's mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi seems sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's lonely being by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try giving her a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just taking a walk with Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were with Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Michiru say anything about the person who was with me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't say anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is your mum, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I once helped her with a cart of grocery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the two of you are rather similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a fragment of that person's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll scrub you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning, Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It seems that I caused you trouble yesterday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you came, Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of work to do today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Kano-san napping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her to rest, in part because of what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time for her to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm writing this because I think that you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally decided to go to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that if I do that, everyone can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I can meet the girl you're searching for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when it'll be, but I'll definitely bring that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be grateful if you can help my sister until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's actually really pushing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,P.S. I'm really sorry for the bruise on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko pikopikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko piko. Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no external injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no trace of bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to be life-threatening, but what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she tried to go to the sky from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, my emotions are acting up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,like I'm nostalgic... or sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lay Kano down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shiraho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that the autumn was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband and I had our first child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At birth, there was a bruise on that child's right wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers said it was ominous, but we never paid them any heed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yakumo cried, I sang him a lullaby that I had learned from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo, who would always stop crying, acted differently one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that the feather was an amulet that God had given to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A war started, and my husband, like many others, didn't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone here pick up a shining feather?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Feathers are soiled, so if you've touched one, show yourself and confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, I fled from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I arrived at this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief priest of the shrine was very kind towards us strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that I could start a new life with Yakumo in this peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that summer, an epidemic spread in the village, killing many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Priest, how is this child's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His fever will come down in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the people of the village believe that you two brought about the epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake to invite the two of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, we worship the Miko-gami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Miko-gami gives a sign to those who bring disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If the villagers hear of this child's bruise, they will clamour for his sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me to sacrifice him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In this land, we have averted disasters by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This child is my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one treasure that my husband left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, you will be killed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,by my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What mother would kill her own child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that child will destroy the world, what mother can bear killing her own child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, somehow, save this child, just this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already full.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'll go home now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because Onee-chan is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as a new friend that I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that he's searching for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that it'd be nice if I were that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's painful, you can always come with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember you very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and I might have cut short your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving birth to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so be happy down there.
