Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san, you saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was that feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, I met Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't go to where she was, but I was able to properly thank her, just as Yukito-kun told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it drift into the sky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bubbles are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really a bother, so I'm always playing by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother lost a vent for her feelings, so she chose to continue watching a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
